              "alt": "Pathfinder #213: Thirst for Blood pg. 81",
              "aonid": 257,
              "game-obj": "Sources",
              "name": "Pathfinder #213: Thirst for Blood pg. 81",
              "type": "link"
            },
            "name": "Pathfinder #213: Thirst for Blood",
            "page": 81,
            "type": "source"
          }
        ],
        "subtype": "equipment",
        "text": "This four-sided prism is imbued with knowledge for the construction of several objects. The stone contains the knowledge of all formulas found in a basic crafter\u2019s book. While you have the stone invested, you have the full knowledge of the stone\u2019s formulas. This counts as having the formula for the purposes of Crafting checks. While you have this knowledge, you can write the formulas down for later use, such as if you lose access to the stone. You also gain a +1 item bonus to skill checks made to Craft while the stone is invested. The resonant power allows you to cast phantasmal minion as an arcane innate spell once per day.",
        "type": "stat_block"
      },
      {
        "level": 4,
        "links": [
          {
            "alt": "invested",
            "aonid": 637,
            "game-obj": "Traits",
            "name": "invested",
            "type": "link"
          },
          {
            "alt": "mending",
            "aonid": 1597,
            "game-obj": "Spells",
            "name": "mending",
            "type": "link"
          }
        ],
        "name": "Aeon Stone (Repairing)",
        "price": {
          "currency": "gp",
          "subtype": "price",
          "text": "75 gp",
          "type": "stat_block_section",
          "value": 75
        },
        "sources": [
          {
            "link": {
              "alt": "Pathfinder #213: Thirst for Blood pg. 82",
              "aonid": 257,
              "game-obj": "Sources",
              "name": "Pathfinder #213: Thirst for Blood pg. 82",
              "type": "link"
            },
            "name": "Pathfinder #213: Thirst for Blood",
            "page": 82,
            "type": "source"
          }
        ],
        "subtype": "equipment",
        "text": "This translucent, spherical stone\u2019s center contains a multitude of sparkling, colored flecks. While you have this stone invested, you gain a +1 item bonus to skill checks made to Craft. Additionally, when Repairing an item, you restore an additional 5 Hit Points to the item (10 Hit Points on a critical success). The resonant power allows you to cast mending as an arcane innate spell once per day.",
        "type": "stat_block"
      },
      {
        "level": 5,
        "links": [
          {
            "alt": "persistent damage",
            "aonid": 29,
            "game-obj": "Conditions",
            "name": "persistent damage",
