            "name": "GM Core",
            "page": 284,
            "type": "source"
          }
        ],
        "subtype": "equipment",
        "text": "This red crystalline star covers you in a faint aura when you are subject to lingering wounds. You gain resistance 3 to persistent damage. At the end of any turn where the persistent damage can't overcome this resistance, end that condition. The resonant power allows you to cast stabilize as a primal innate cantrip.",
        "type": "stat_block"
      },
